{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Screen.onorientationchange","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientationchange_event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen_Orientation_API\">Screen Orientation API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/availHeight\"><code>availHeight</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/availLeft\"><code>availLeft</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/availTop\"><code>availTop</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/availWidth\"><code>availWidth</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/colorDepth\"><code>colorDepth</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/height\"><code>height</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/left\"><code>left</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/mozBrightness\"><code>mozBrightness</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/mozEnabled\"><code>mozEnabled</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientation\"><code>orientation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/pixelDepth\"><code>pixelDepth</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>Screen: orientationchange event</code></em></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/top\"><code>top</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/width\"><code>width</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/lockOrientation\"><code>lockOrientation()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/unlockOrientation\"><code>unlockOrientation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Screen Orientation API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientation\"><code>Screen.orientation</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation\"><code>ScreenOrientation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard deprecated\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>非推奨:</strong> この機能は非推奨になりました。まだ対応しているブラウザーがあるかもしれませんが、すでに関連するウェブ標準から削除されているか、削除の手続き中であるか、互換性のためだけに残されている可能性があります。使用を避け、できれば既存のコードは更新してください。このページの下部にある<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">互換性一覧表</a>を見て判断してください。この機能は突然動作しなくなる可能性があることに注意してください。</p></div><p></p>\n\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>警告:</strong> これは標準外で非推奨の機能であり、 Firefox だけが異なる名前で実装されていました。代わりに <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation\"><code>ScreenOrientation.onchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> を使用してください。</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Screen オブジェクトに送信される <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/orientationchange_event\" title=\"orientationchange\"><code>orientationchange</code></a> イベントのイベントハンドラーです。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">screen.onorientationchange = <var>funcRef</var>;\n</pre>\n\n<p>ここで <code>funcRef</code> は関数への参照です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/screen-orientation/published/20140220.html#extensions-to-the-screen-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Screen Orientation API<br><small lang=\"ja\">onorientationchange の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義 (草稿には既に存在しません)</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Screen.onorientationchange","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientationchange_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/orientationchange_event\" title=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/orientationchange\">orientationchange</a></code></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model/Managing_screen_orientation\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">画面の向きの管理 (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Screen オブジェクトに送信される orientationchange イベントのイベントハンドラーです。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Screen: orientationchange event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"window.screen.onorientationchange","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/screen/orientationchange_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/screen/orientationchange_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen","title":"Screen"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientationchange_event","title":"Screen.onorientationchange"}],"pageTitle":"Screen.onorientationchange - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}